Source:  Taranaki Herald
Author:
Vol / Page:  3
Edition:
Quote:  With the exception of about 30 acres of bush, this property is all good fern land with a quantity of natural and artificial grasses growing amongst it; there is some fencing erected thereon, and with the aid of the river and stream boundaries, very little more fencing is required to complete the whole in a ring fence.
