Vol / Page:  4
Edition:
Quote:  Mr. St. George will sell about 20 Acres ( more or less) of Excellent Land, situated on the BELL BLOCK, price GBP60. Or will Let it on a Term, for a nominal rental, upon consideration that the Tenant will erect a ring fence, consisting of a Ditch and a two-feet bank, planted with furze, with a Rail on the top.
