Vol / Page:  77
Edition:
Quote:  (1.) The lessee shall, within two years from the date of his lease, have the land fenced with a ring-fence; and such fence shall be a sufficient fence within the meaning of `The Fencing Act, 1895.'  (Vide `Fencing Act.')
